<item>
            <title>[SPR-2538] PersistenceUnitReader.findSchemaResource should do classpath*:**/ search last</title>
                <link>https://jira.spring.io/browse/SPR-2538</link>
                <project id="10000" key="SPR">Spring Framework</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Because classpath*:**/ can cause problems in different environments perhaps it would be a good idea to do the global search last after org and com or catch file not found exceptions when searching the root.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;See &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.spring.io/browse/SPR-2537&quot; title=&quot;classpath*:**/  fails in websphere 6.1&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;SPR-2537&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;SPR-2537&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
